播的他的私人事务有关”。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/riize-dreamy-love-119-music-video-3566032">新秀男孩乐队 RIIZE 带着梦幻般的“Love 119”音乐视频回归，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
发行商因秘密更改战利品箱掉落率被罚款 700 万英镑https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/publisher-fined-7million-for-secretly-changing-loot-box-drop-rates-3566022?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=publisher-fined-7million-秘密改变战利品箱掉落率Ali ShutlerFri, 05 Jan 2024 09:29:57 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsPC https://www.nme.com/?p=3566022 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="冒险岛截图" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Nexon 被韩国反垄断监管机构罚款</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/publisher-fined-7million-for-secretly-changing-loot-box-drop-rates-3566022">出版商因秘密更改战利品箱掉落率而被罚款 700 万英镑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="冒险岛截图" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/MapleStory-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>韩国发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nexon">Nexon</a>因秘密更改战利品箱掉落率而被罚款 116 亿韩元（700 万英镑）。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/heartsteel-exo-baekhyun-riot-games-league-of-legends-virtual-artists-3562214">Heartsteel 上的 Riot Games：“Baekhyun 和 Ezreal 的合作是一个梦想”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据韩国反垄断监管机构称，Nexon 在 2010 年至 2021 年间“多次”更改了 2D MMORPG <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/maplestory"><em>MapleStory</em></a>和<em>Bubble Fighter</em>中战利品箱的费率（来自<em><a href="https://www.pcgamer.com/nexon-fined-nearly-dollar9m-for-falsifying-loot-box-drop-rates/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PCGamer</a></em> ），违反了韩国《电子商务消费者保护法》。</p><p>在<em>MapleStory</em>中，战利品盒被称为立方体，于 2010 年首次推出。这些随机立方体的售价为每个 2,000 ₩（1.20 英镑），用于改变各种游戏内物品的力量。然而，在推出后不久，Nexcon 在没有通知玩家的情况下改变了提供更强大立方体的频率。 2011 年 8 月，发行商发表了一份声明，否认对掉落率进行更改。</p><p>此次 700 万英镑的罚款是韩国公平贸易委员会开出的最大一笔罚款，此前 Nexon 曾于 2018 年因在战利品箱掉落率方面误导<em>《突然袭击 2》</em>玩家而被处以 69 万英镑罚款。</p><p> “我们处以最大一笔罚款是因为[立方体]是<em>冒险岛</em>的核心产品，违规期限较长，这是继<em>《突然袭击》</em>之后[Nexon]的第二次违规，”韩国公平贸易委员会市场监督部主任金正基在一份声明中解释。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="活出你的故事 |冒险岛新纪元将于 11 月 15 日推出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/2yw4BO0yu-U?start=1&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>英国大学 2022 年的一份报告声称， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/loot-boxes-cause-financial-and-emotional-harm-to-children-3358227">战利品箱会对儿童造成“经济和情感伤害”</a> ，并且只应向 18 岁或以上的人开放。去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/european-parliament-votes-to-crack-down-on-loot-boxes-and-gold-farming-3383033">欧洲议会投票赞成打击电子游戏中的战利品箱</a>，而由于对战利品箱的监管更加严格， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/diablo-immortal">《暗黑破坏神：不朽》</a></em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/diablo-immortal-not-being-released-in-countries-that-ban-loot-boxes-3233249">从未在比利时或荷兰发行</a>。发行商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/activision-blizzard">动视暴雪</a>也因未披露<em>《暗黑破坏神：不朽》中战利品箱的存在而被欧洲评级委员会 PEGI 罚款。</em></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/epic-games">Epic Games</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fortnite-studio-hit-with-201million-fine-and-ordered-to-stop-tricking-players-3413448#:~:text=The%20United%20States%20Federal%20Trade,you%20can%20play%20in%202023%3F">与美国政府达成了 2 亿英镑的和解</a>，退还儿童购买的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fortnite"><em>《堡垒之夜》</em></a> 。</p><p>在其他消息中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-hacker-gary-bowser-gets-early-release-from-40-month-prison-sentence-3432034">黑客加里·鲍泽（Gary Bowser）</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-hacker-gary-bowser-denies-involvement-with-switch-flash-cart-3565214">否认参与</a>了新披露的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/nintendo-switch">任天堂 Switch</a>闪存车。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/publisher-fined-7million-for-secretly-changing-loot-box-drop-rates-3566022">出版商因秘密更改战利品箱掉落率而被罚款 700 万英镑的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
