ntent/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Gallagher_Squire_BTS_NME-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/john-squire">约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire)</a>分享了他们期待已久的首张合作单曲“Just Another Rainbow”——请在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-gallagher-john-squire-just-another-rainbow-review-3565653"><strong>阅读更多：</strong>利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 和约翰·斯奎尔 (John Squire)：曼彻斯特偶像在《Just Another Rainbow》中碰撞——但这有什么好处吗？</a></li></ul><p>经过几个月的调侃后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-and-john-squire-confirm-album-and-announce-single-just-another-rainbow-3561878">上个月正式宣布</a>——加拉格尔称赞他们即将发行的唱片是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-teases-joint-album-with-john-squire-as-the-best-record-since-the-beatles-revolver-3520505">“自披头士乐队的《左轮手枪》以来最好的唱片”——</a>前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">绿洲乐队</a>主唱和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-stone-roses">石玫瑰</a>乐队吉他手今天（一月）首次试听该项目5）以迷幻主打单曲“Just Another Rainbow”的形式。</p><p>以标志性的花香但嘎吱作响的 Squires riff 开头，然后 Gallagher 咆哮道“<em>我可能知道这只是另一条彩虹</em>”，这首歌很快就发展成为一首 60 年代的精神歌曲，并配有哀嚎和仰望星空的吉他独奏。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify 嵌入：又一条彩虹" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="152" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/track/2xE7912IhBp4poxLjOS6WJ?si=8a78f0f540b54906&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/liam-gallagher-john-squire-just-another-rainbow-review-3565653"><em>NME</em>对《Just Another Rainbow》的评论</a>指出，这首歌“愿意伸展和律动，与流行音乐驱动的‘ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/liam-gallagher-cmon-you-know-3231721">C&#39;Mon You Know</a> ’[加拉格尔的 2022 年个人专辑]不一致”——并指出“暗示” “Squire 的表演和结构中的 Cream”，甚至还有 Liam 慢吞吞的方式中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-rolling-stones">滚石乐队</a>的一些东西： <i>“只是另一道彩虹，悬挂在我上方/只是另一道彩虹，落在我的树上”</i> 。</p><p> 《Just Another Rainbow》的推出提前了二人组承诺的“随着今年的展开，将推出更多新音乐”。该单曲可<a href="https://gallaghersquire.lnk.to/JustAnotherRainbow" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订 7 英寸黑胶唱片。</p><p>视频正在制作中，两人本周分享了以下预告片。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C1myJictoah/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.